The paper deals with machine learning algorithms and regression using kernel techniques, which are commonly studied in the subfield of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the Complexity Approximation Principle, which is a concept often used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of the algorithm to image processing and computer vision (cs.CV) is also mentioned. Additionally, the paper involves the use of neural networks (cs.NE) and online algorithms (cs.DS).
